>   arch/s390/kvm/gmap.c | 56 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
>   3 files changed, 52 insertions(+), 54 deletions(-)
> 

Ugh, you moved it AND changed it.
Please don't do that if you want to have patches reviewed.
Or at least provide a diff between the changes.


